n\n教师详细信息</big><div class=\"fr\">当前位置：\n                        <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n                <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../yjry/jy.htm\">研究人员</a>\n                <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../yjry/jsxxxx.htm\">教师详细信息</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<section class=\"n_container\">\n    <section class=\"n_left fl\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n        <section class=\"n_news_detail\">\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/js/photoswipe/3.0.5.1/photoswipe.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/photoswipe/3.0.5.1/klass.min.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n<div class=\"ar_article_box\">\n    <div class=\"nav01\">\n        <h3>杨振宁</h3>\n        <h6>\n            <span>日期：<font>2020-12-21</font></span>\n            <span>浏览量：<font><script>_showDynClicks(\"wbnews\", 1703716603, 1213)</script><span id=\"dynclicks_wbnews_1213_31\" name=\"dynclicks_wbnews_1213_31\">22530</span></font></span>\n        </h6>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"vsb_content\" class=\"ar_article\"><div class=\"v_news_content\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;\">\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_img\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"260\" src=\"/__local/6/A3/F5/C02D2690665DC304198D6DEC83D_95025896_706E.jpg?e=.jpg\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" title=\"\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/6A3F5C02D2690665DC304198D6DEC83D/95025896/706E?e=.jpg\" vheight=\" 260px\" vwidth=\" 200px\" orisrc=\"/__local/6/A3/F5/C02D2690665DC304198D6DEC83D_95025896_706E.jpg?e=.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\" style=\"width: 200px; height: 260px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>杨振宁</strong></p>\n<p><strong> 名誉院长、教授</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"../../yangzhenningdashinianbiao_2022.pdf\" target=\"_self\"><strong>杨振宁大事年表</strong></a></p>\n<h4><p>教育背景</p></h4>\n<p>学士, 西南联合大学, 1942</p>\n<p>硕士, 清华大学, 1944</p>\n<p>博士, 美国芝加哥大学, 1948</p>\n<h4><p>工作履历</p></h4>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">美国普林斯顿高等学术研究所研究员</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">, 1949-1955</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">美国普林斯顿高等学术研究所教授</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">, 1955-1966</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">美国纽约州立大学石溪分校爱因斯坦讲座教授</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">, 1966-1999</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">香港中文大学博文讲座教授</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">, 1986-</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">清华大学教授</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">, 1999-</span></p>\n<h4><p>研究领域</p></h4>\n<p>粒子物理、场论、统计物理、凝聚态物理</p>\n<h4><p>研究概况</p></h4>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\">1954年，与米尔斯提出“杨-米尔斯规范场论”，奠定了后来粒子物理标准模型的基础，被认为是现代物理学的基石之一。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">1956</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">年，与李政道合作提出弱作用中宇称不守恒的革命性思想，并获得</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">1957年诺贝尔物理学奖。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">1967</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">年，发现解决一维量子多体问题的关键方程式，</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">1972</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">年与巴克斯特提出“杨</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">-巴克斯特方程”，开辟了统计物理和量子群等物理和数学研究的新方向。</span></p>\n<h4><p>奖励与荣誉</p></h4>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">诺贝尔奖（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">Nobel Prize, Physics</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">, 1957</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">润福德奖（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">Rumford</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">, 1980</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">美国国家科学奖章（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">U.S. National Medal of Science</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">, 1986</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">富兰克林奖章（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">Benjamin Franklin Medal</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">, 1993</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">鲍尔奖（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">Bower Award</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">, 1994</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">中国国际科技合作奖</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">, 1995</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">波哥柳波夫奖（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">N. Bogoliubov Prize</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">, 1996</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">昂萨格奖（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">Lars Onsager Prize</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">, 1999</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">费萨尔国王国际科学奖（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">King Faisal International Prize</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">, 2001</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">求是终身成就奖，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">2019</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">美国国家科学院外籍院士</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">英国皇家学会外籍会员</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">伦敦</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\">)</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">俄罗斯科学院外籍院士</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; line-height: 30px; vertical-align: top; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333333\">中国科学院院士</span></p>\n<h4><p>学术成果</p></h4>\n<p><a href=\"/__local/0/C6/0F/84B74A051A42FF8E820E231CB89_AAC510D5_80C52.pdf?e=.pdf\">Scientific and Related Works of Chen Ning Yang</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><br></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">[42a] C. N. Yang. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Group Theory and the Vibration of Polyatomic Molecules.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">B.Sc. thesis, National Southwest Associated University (1942).</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">[44a] C. N. Yang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">On the Uniqueness of Young's Differentials.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Bull. Amer. Math. Soc. 50, 373 (1944).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">[44b] C. N. Yang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Variation of Interaction Energy with Change of Lattice Constants and Change of Degree of Order.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Chinese J. of Phys. 5, 138 (1944).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">[44c] C. N. Yang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Investigations in the Statistical Theory of Superlattices.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">M.Sc. thesis, National Tsing Hua University (1944).</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">[45a] C. N. Yang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">A Generalization of the Quasi-Chemical Method in the Statistical Theory of Superlattices. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">J. Chem. Phys. 13, 66 (1945).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">[45b] C. N. Yang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">The Critical Temperature and Discontinuity of Specific Heat of a Superlattice. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Chinese J. Phys. 6, 59 (1945).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">[46a] James Alexander, Geoffrey Chew, Walter Salove, Chen Yang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Translation of the 1933 Pauli article “Relativistic Quantum Mechanics” in Handbuch der Physik, volume 14, Part II; Chapter 2, Section B.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">[47a] C. N. Yang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">On Quantized Space-Time. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Phys. Rev. 72, 874 (1947).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">[47b] C. N. Yang and Y. Y. Li.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">General Theory of the Quasi-Chemical Method in the Statistical Theory of Superlattices. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Chinese J. Phys. 7, 59 (1947).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">[48a] C. N. Yang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">On the Angular Distribution in Nuclear Reactions and Coincidence Measurements. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Phys. Rev. 74, 764 (1948).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">[48b] S. K. Allison, H. V. Argo, W. R. Arnold, L. del Rosario, H. A. Wilcox <span class=\"fontstyle0\">and C. N. Yang.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Measurement of Short Range Nuclear Recoils from Disintegrations of the Light Elements.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Phys. Rev. 74, 1233 (1948).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">[48c] C. N. Yang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">On the Angular Distribution in Nuclear Reactions and Coincidence Measurements.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Ph.D. thesis, University of Chicago (1948).</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">[49a] T. D. Lee, M. Rosenbluth and C. N. Yang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Interaction of Mesons with Nucleons and Light Particles. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Phys. Rev. 75, 905 (1949).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle3\">介子與核子和輕粒子的相互作用</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle3\">《</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">20</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">世紀上半葉中國物理學論文集粹》 </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">,</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">戴念祖編</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">, </span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">湖南教育出版社</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">(1993), p. 1218-1219.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">[49b] E. Fermi and C. N. Yang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Are Mesons Elementary Particles?</p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Phys. Rev. 76, 1739 (1949).</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:'arial',sans-serif;color:#333333\"></span><br></p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\"><br></p>\n</div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n        \n        <section id=\"ar_fot\">\n            <h1 class=\"highlight prev\"><a href=\"1214.htm\"><span>上一篇：</span>翟荟</a></h1>\n            <h1 class=\"highlight next\"><a href=\"1205.htm\"><span>下一篇：</span>姚期智</a></h1>\n            <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n        </section>\n   \n    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div>\n</form>\n</section>\n        <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n    </section>\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"clear\"></div